subject: Sailboats and Sailing
Olympic Games (2012)
Swimming
lead_paragraph: Although Australia's swimmers did not win an individual event at the 2012 Olympics in London, its sailors won three gold medals and continued to be at the thrill-seeking heart of the next America's Cup.
